136
00:11:16,092 --> 00:11:17,051
<font color="japanese">グンサン

137
00:11:17,635 --> 00:11:18,886
<font color="japanese">便秘らしいな

138
00:11:18,969 --> 00:11:19,970
<font color="japanese">これを飲め

139
00:11:20,054 --> 00:11:21,138
<font color="japanese">サンキュー…

